        ],
        "notes": "JS2IL resolves `extends Array` to the runtime CLR base type JavaScriptRuntime.Array. `super(...)` in derived constructors calls Array::.ctor() and then applies JS Array constructor semantics via Array.ConstructInto(args). Limitation: only `extends Array` is handled today; other intrinsic bases are not yet supported."
